# MIDAS Integration Test Credentials
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# No credentials needed for interactive mode (default).
#
# Just run:
#   cd testing && python -m pytest integration/ -q -s
#
# A browser window opens. Log in with your corporate SSO.
# pytest waits, then runs all tests automatically.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# OPTION A — Static token (skip browser entirely)
# Copy auth_token from browser DevTools → Application → LocalStorage
# MIDAS_ACCESS_TOKEN=eyJ...
#
# OPTION B — Automated login (no browser interaction)
# MIDAS_SSO_EMAIL=first.last@exlservice.com
# MIDAS_SSO_PASSWORD=your-password-here
#
# TUNING (all optional)
# MIDAS_BASE_URL=https://exldecision-ai-dev.exlservice.com
# PLAYWRIGHT_NAV_TIMEOUT_MS=300000
# PLAYWRIGHT_SLOW_MO_MS=0
# MIDAS_HTTP_TIMEOUT=120
